EasyFly Flight System
=====================================

EasyFly is a flight maintenance and booking system. It allows different kinds of authorized users to schedule and maintain airports, airlines, routes and flights. 
It also allows customers to check flight schedules and availability, book tickets, select seats, and generate boarding passes.

Languages / tools / technologies used:
- Play Framework for Java
- Oracle
- Bootstrap
- JQuery

To run this application you need:
1. VPN connection to the Swinburne network
2. Play framework installed
3. If you are running this with a fresh Oracle account, first run schema.sql and proc.sql on the new account, and change the credentials in the configuration file (application.conf) 